name: Silencer
description: It works by using the pulses of high pressure created when exhaust is expelled from the combustion chamber. name: Engine

name: Engine Gard
description: Engine guards are hoop shaped bars usually mounted on motorcycle frames at the front in order to protect the engine mainly and also to protect the rider for bike accidents at slower speeds. Engine guards are also called as 'Crash Bars'.
